| **ClusterMapping.gpkg** | `ClusterMapping` | 50 | MultiPolygon | cluster name, total growers, species planted, survival rates, restored areas. |
| **CarbonProjectTreeMeasurement.gpkg** | `CarbonProjectTreeMeasurement` | 65 | Point | DBH (Diameter at Breast Height), height, canopy cover, species name, date, monitor. |
| **SeedCollection.gpkg** | `SeedCollection` | 34 | Point | seed species collected, canopy, quantity, viability %, collection method, rainfall/temp. |
| **Infrastracture Verfications.gpkg** | `Infrastracture Verfications` | 14 | Point | infrastructure type, stage, assessor, region, photos. |
| **SeedBank.gpkg** | `SeedBank` | 11 | Point | bank name, capacity, quantity available, species 1–15. |
| **Infrastructure.gpkg** | `Infrastructure` | 9 | Point | assessment type, observations, stakeholders, recommendations. |
| **CarbonProjectValidationPlots.gpkg** | `CarbonProjectValidationPlots` | 3 | Point | validation plots, tree radii (5m/10m), species, dbh, canopy, height, grower. |
| **Kariba Red++.gpkg** | `kariba_red__kariba_red_` | 1 | MultiPolygon | REDD+ project area boundary polygon. |
| **ApiarySiteAssessment.gpkg** | `ApiarySiteAssessment` | 0 | Point | *(Template/Placeholder for apiary site monitoring)* |
